            must maintain active <strong>General Liability</strong> and <strong
              >Workers' Compensation</strong
            > insurance specific to tree services. This protects you from being held
            liable for onsite injuries or accidental property damage.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-icon">üìú</div>
        <div>
          <h3>State & Local Compliance</h3>
          <p>
