        or receives consistent negative feedback regarding professional conduct,
        they are immediately removed from our dispatch list. We represent the
        homeowner first.
      </p>
      <div
        style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 20px;"
      >
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-weight: 800; color: #1b4332;"
        >
          <span style="color: #16a34a;">‚úî</span> Verified Licenses
